{"tid":1683190,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【震懾班黑警?】武警深圳灣集結演練　有裝甲車水炮車在場","createTime":"2019-10-30T13:54:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T14:16:57.000Z","uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6c999b9c97c68d9d3f94067eb088dbb39a95e01c","tid":1683190,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:54:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191030/photo/bkn-20191030183359044-1030_00822_001_01b.jpg?20191030193313\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191030%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191030183359044-1030_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20191030193313&h=6e04f4cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n持續超過4個月的修例風波至今未息，且引發多場暴力衝突。美國傳媒周三（30日）報道刊登一批照片，顯示在廣東深圳市的深圳灣體育中心附近，有大批疑為武警的軍人展開演習。圖中所見，該批身穿防暴裝備的武警，在演習現場與持械人士展開訓練，亦有武警模擬為同袍包紮，同場亦有水炮車出動。<br />\n<br />\n從該批照片可見，有武警手持棍狀武器和盾牌的裝備，與戴上頭盔的同袍展開搏鬥訓練；另有一批武警在場內，為模擬頭部受傷的同袍包紮傷口。此外，演習現場亦出動了一批水炮車和裝甲車，其中有水炮車在現場噴水。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191030/photo/bkn-20191030183359044-1030_00822_001_06b.jpg?20191030193313\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191030%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191030183359044-1030_00822_001_06b.jpg%3F20191030193313&h=5f1cc3bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191030/photo/bkn-20191030183359044-1030_00822_001_03b.jpg?20191030193313\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191030%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191030183359044-1030_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20191030193313&h=b73f38c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191030/bkn-20191030183359044-1030_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191030%2Fbkn-20191030183359044-1030_00822_001.html&d=VY3E9QkOBFFWjsPhNJvPHstNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=c8c074df\" target=\"_blank\">https://h